name: Jack O'Lanterns 01 - James Reeves' Ghost Ship
description:
All vessels wherein men have sailed and died
Are haunted ships. Through the open hatches
The harmless phantoms on their errands glide,
With feet that make no sound upon the deck.

-- adapted from Henry Wadsworth Longfellow, ‘Haunted Houses’

Halloween 2021 single hand carved and etched pumpkin tribute to @Flygohr's Tezos Pirates
